data.description:
Outstanding Investment Opportunity: Originally a 3-bedroom residence, the owners have initiated an impressive expansion project, introducing a new primary bedroom and an en suite primary bath. This property serves as a blank canvas for the next homeowner's vision. The primary en suite bath is already framed, with rough plumbing and electrical work completed. The foundation and piers have been initiated at the rear of the residence, although the inspection was not passed and has since expired.

Situated on a beautiful nearly 1/2 acre lot, the property includes an outbuilding, wired shop, tractor shed, and chicken coop—all negotiable for inclusion. Noteworthy features encompass a new roof installed in 2016, a fully sealed crawlspace with new plumbing, a new 200 amp service implemented in 2020, and HVAC replacement in the same year, complete with a new air filtration system.  Don't let this opportunity pass, property is listed under current tax value. INTERIOR PHOTOS COMING 02-10-2024
